OL,3,CCouncil workers sent strike ballots in
OL,4,C'biggest vote of its kind in years'
OL,6,FTens of thousands of council workers
OL,7,Fwill be balloted on strike action from
OL,8,FThursday in what a union is calling
OL,9,Fthe biggest vote of its kind in years.
OL,11,FUnison said a vote will be offered to
OL,12,Fmore than 80,000 workers across all of
OL,13,FScotland's 32 councils.
OL,15,FStaff will choose whether to stage
OL,16,Fwalkouts as they continue a dispute
OL,17,Fwith local authorities over pay. The
OL,18,Fballot will close on June 12.
OL,20,FIt follows a recent consultation in
OL,21,Fwhich 92% backed strike action.
