OL,3,CCouncil workers sent strike ballots in
OL,4,C'biggest vote of its kind in years'
OL,6,FLocal government employer body Cosla
OL,7,Fhas offered all council workers in
OL,8,FScotland a 3% increase for 2025-26,
OL,9,Fless than half of the union's request
OL,10,Ffor a 6.5% pay rise.
OL,12,FUnison Scotland co-lead for local
OL,13,Fgovernment, David O'Connor, said:
OL,14,F"Dedicated council staff have seen the
OL,15,Fvalue of their pay fall for more than
OL,16,Fa decade, as wages failed to keep pace
OL,17,Fwith the cost of living.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
