OL,3,CCouncil workers sent strike ballots in
OL,4,C'biggest vote of its kind in years'
OL,6,F"These workers deliver high-quality,
OL,7,Fvital services to communities, despite
OL,8,Fincreasing pressures, dwindling
OL,9,Fresources and significant staffing
OL,10,Fshortages.
OL,12,F"Cosla's offer only adds to the real
OL,13,Ffinancial hardship faced by employees,
OL,14,Fespecially with rent, council tax and
OL,15,Fenergy bills continuing to soar.
OL,17,F"Strike action is always a last
OL,18,Fresort, but local government workers
OL,19,Fhave been underpaid and undervalued
OL,20,Ffor far too long.
