OL,3,CCouncil workers sent strike ballots in
OL,4,C'biggest vote of its kind in years'
OL,6,F"Cosla and the Scottish government
OL,7,Fneed to step up and offer a decent
OL,8,Fwage increase that reflects the value
OL,9,Fof these workers."
OL,11,FSusanne Gens, chair of Unison
OL,12,FScotland's local government committee,
OL,13,Fadded: "Staff have indicated
OL,14,Foverwhelmingly that they've reached
OL,15,Ftheir limit. They can't afford to
OL,16,Fshoulder the burden of real-terms pay
OL,17,Fcuts.
