OL,3,CCouncil workers sent strike ballots in
OL,4,C'biggest vote of its kind in years'
OL,6,F"Local government workers are the glue
OL,7,Fthat holds communities together and
OL,8,Fprovide essential services on which
OL,9,Feveryone relies.
OL,11,F"The Scottish Government and Cosla
OL,12,Fmust recognise their worth and respond
OL,13,Fwith a fair pay offer that values
OL,14,Fthese essential workers."
OL,16,FCosla has been approached for comment.
